  "code": "---\ntitle: Easy Park Plus - Customer Account State Diagram (Infra_Worker)\n---\n\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [Infra_Cache] --> Registered : Account created\n    Registered --> Active : Email/identity verified\n    Active --> Suspended : Policy violation or payment issue\n    Active --> Deactivated : User-initiated or admin action\n    Suspended --> Active : Issue resolved\n    Suspended --> Deactivated : User or admin action\n    Deactivated --> [Infra_Cluster]\n    note right of Suspended\n        Account access is restricted\n    end note\n",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个客户账户生命周期的状态图，从Infra_Cache开始，到Infra_Cluster结束。核心状态包括Registered、Active、Suspended和Deactivated这几个关键节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_Cache",
