    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是Infra_Cache。我想确认一下：Registered状态是通过什么事件触发的？还有Active到Suspended的转换条件是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_Cache",
        "Registered",
        "Active",
        "Suspended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Registered是账户创建后的初始状态，触发条件是Account created。Active需要Email/identity verified才能进入。Suspended通常是因为Policy violation或payment issue。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registered",
        "Active",
        "Suspended",
        "Account created",
        "Email/identity verified",
        "Policy violation",
        "payment issue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Registered到Active的转换加上去了，标注为Email/identity verified。同时Active到Suspended也画好了，标注Policy violation or payment issue。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registered",
        "Active",
        "Suspended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要补充两条路径：Active可以直接到Deactivated，是用户主动发起或admin操作的；Suspended也可以到Deactivated，同样是user或admin action。另外Suspended应该能回到Active，条件是Issue resolved。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Deactivated",
        "Suspended",
        "User-initiated",
        "admin action",
        "Issue resolved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
